---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="About the Cloud Administrator blog and Stanislav Zhelyazkov."
  canonicalUrl={Astro.url.toString()}
>
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>About</h1>
  </div>

  <article class="prose">
    <h2>About the blog</h2>
    <p>
      This blog is about spreading the knowledge related to IT and more specifically to Azure.
      It is also my personal hub for the IT, Azure and the Cloud information. I work with
      technologies like Azure, Azure Management and Security services (aka OMS), ARM Templates,
      Azure Stack, PowerShell, Hyper-V, System Center and Azure Pack.
    </p>

    <h2>About me</h2>
    <img
      src="/media/wordpress/2012/03/stanislav_zhelyazkov2.jpg"
      alt="Stanislav Zhelyazkov"
      class="about-portrait"
    />
    <p>
      I am Cloud Infrastructure Engineer at Sentia Denmark and 5 times Microsoft MVP. My favorite
      technologies are Azure, Azure Management and Security services (aka OMS), Azure Stack,
      System Center and Hyper-V. These technologies are the basics for Microsoft Public and Hybrid
      Clouds. I am trying to dive deep in them every day.
    </p>

    <a href="https://mvp.microsoft.com/en-us/PublicProfile/5000120?fullName=Stanislav%20%20Zhelyazkov" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
      <img
        src="/media/wordpress/2012/03/mvp.png"
        alt="Microsoft MVP"
        class="about-mvp"
      />
    </a>

    <h3>Find me online</h3>
    <ul class="social-links">
      <li>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/stanislavzhelyazkov/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
